{"tid":1543103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擺左係個心入面兩個月，今日終於可以講出來","createTime":"2019-09-05T05:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T05:42:55.000Z","uid":293778,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4055760f79e8c1ad50454648f2037dbc98cdd39a","tid":1543103,"uid":293778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:23:17.000Z","msg":"係，兩個月來佢一支低調咁支持一班前線，無論物資上同戰略上面都俾左好多幫助大家。<br />\n因為佢既身份問題，佢係呢件事上面受左好多委屈，我地一班知道佢立場既人都好想幫佢公開澄清，等大家知道佢係真香港人。<br />\n但佢唔俾我地咁做，因為佢係佢既團體入面仲有好多使命未完成。<br />\n睇過無間道既人都知，做臥底好難，兩面都唔係人，義鼠為左香港所做既付出係我地普通人難以想像。<br />\n今日你肯企出來，話俾大家知你過去一段時間默默做既嘢，我地一班前線亦都終於可以將呢個秘密講出來，加油，芬芬，無論大陸點睇你，我地都會同你一齊行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7x9hpvE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7x9hpvE.jpg&h=0c487de3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"856f30c4930c4224b0d0f80644436addda765aa4","tid":1543103,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:23:30.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\